,Recommended,211900,2546218,"Posted: 29 October, 2012",all,Aurumlamina,"A classic-style strategy game with a massive number of classes to choose from.  Each of the unique classes have their own strengths and weaknesses that provide a high level of entertainment.  The economy system is extremely innovative as different classes (armies) gather different types of resources from the same terrain.  For example, a Baron (the knightly themed army) gathers an increased amount of gold from his villages and towns but finds little of value on forest squares, while a Druid gathers plants from the wild to produce his special units.A very unique, yet nostalgic feel to this game.  I highly recommend it."
